getVector <- function(vv,bInd,l)
{
  c <- vector()
  if (bInd > 1)
  {
    c <- rep(NA,bInd-1)
  }
  res <- c(c,vv)
  cc <- vector()
  cc <- rep(NA,l-length(res))
  res <- c(res,cc)
  return(res)
  
}
